George L. PACE v. Guy T. HELVERING, Commissioner of Internal Revenue. No. 1426. Circuit Court of Appeals, Tenth Circuit. June 1, 1936. Don T. Haynes, of Wichita Falls, Tex., for petitioner. Thomas J.- Morrissey, U. S. Atty., of Denver, Col., for respondent.

Before LEWIS and PHILLIPS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Petition for review dismissed for failure to prosecute.
